# Repo context

This repository holds **multiple** Plastic Antweight / SPARC-oriented combat robots and **accessories** (software, firmware, PCBs, CAD, 3D prints, documentation).

## PCB

- Design PCBs in **KiCad** (`.kicad_pro`, schematics, layouts).
- Prefer **per-project** boards under `bots/<name>/` or `accessories/<name>/`; put **reusable** symbols, footprints, and 3D models under `shared/kicad-libraries/`.

## Layout

- **Bots**: `bots/<robot-name>/`
- **Accessories / side projects**: `accessories/<project-name>/`
- **Shared assets**: `shared/` (libraries, templates, cross-project tools)
- **General docs**: `docs/` (reference vs build notes)

When adding new work, pick the smallest folder that fits; avoid dumping unrelated files at repo root unless they are top-level specs or launch helpers.

## Changes

Keep new structure consistent with the README; split reusable pieces into `shared/` instead of duplicating under every bot.
